  <body>
    <p>A variety of actions are available in the DocBook 5 framework that can be added to the
        <uicontrol>DocBook5</uicontrol> menu, the <uicontrol>Author custom actions</uicontrol>
      toolbar, the contextual menu, and the <uicontrol>Content Completion Assistant</uicontrol>. The
      following default actions are readily available on the <uicontrol>DocBook (Author Custom
        Actions)</uicontrol> toolbar when editing in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode (by default,
      most of them are also available in the <uicontrol>DocBook5</uicontrol> menu and the contextual
      menu):</p>
